      "Help on class Usb in module escpos.printer:\n",
      "\n",
      "class Usb(escpos.escpos.Escpos)\n",
      " |  Usb(idVendor, idProduct, timeout=0, in_ep=130, out_ep=1, *args, **kwargs)\n",
      " |  \n",
      " |  USB printer\n",
      " |  \n",
      " |  This class describes a printer that natively speaks USB.\n",
      " |  \n",
      " |  inheritance:\n",
      " |  \n",
      " |  .. inheritance-diagram:: escpos.printer.Usb\n",
      " |      :parts: 1\n",
      " |  \n",
